data.description: Wonderful opportunity to make this home your own.  Enjoy your privacy on this  expansive open lot located on a quiet cul de sac.  Enter into a grand foyer with ample  natural light drawing you to the beautiful stone raised hearth fireplace in this custom living room design.  Formal dining room leading to modern eat-in kitchen with center island and half bath. Enjoy the view from the family room with french doors opening to the full sized rear deck with landscaped patio and in ground pool and hot tub, perfect for those funtime family barbecues or to just enjoy the peace with your favorite book, Second floor offers master bedroom and bath. Three additional bedrooms and hall bath. Lower level in law suite with full kitchen, living room with stone fireplace, large bedroom and full tiled bath adding to the flexability  of this spacious traditional home. Two car attached garage.
